title: Ep 5: Uhh... Occupied
description:
Today's Proceedings: An incel who gets his way, a man walked in on during his "free time," and a man with unusual bathroom habits.  We also discuss a few personal accounts of our "free time" being interrupted as well as our experience with Be the Match.
